DocAttribute.Name: ShearAreaZ
DocAttribute.Documentation: Area of the profile for calculating the shear stress for a shear force parallel to the profile's Z-axis. Usually measured in [mm2].

DocAttribute.Name: ShearAreaY
DocAttribute.Documentation: Area of the profile for calculating the shear stress for a shear force parallel to the profile's Y-axis. Usually measured in [mm2].

DocAttribute.Name: PlasticShapeFactorY
DocAttribute.Documentation: Ratio of plastic versus elastic bending moment capacity (about y-axis) of the profile.

DocAttribute.Name: PlasticShapeFactorZ
DocAttribute.Documentation: Ratio of plastic versus elastic bending moment capacity (about z-axis) of the profile.
